Privacy Policy for PageSage

Data Collection:
- PageSage extracts webpage content only when you actively use the extension
- Your API keys are stored locally on your device using Chrome's storage API
- Chat history is stored locally per webpage URL

Data Transmission:
- Webpage content and your questions are sent to your chosen AI provider (Groq, Google, OpenAI, or xAI)
- No data is sent to PageSage servers - we don't have any servers

Data Storage:
- All data is stored locally on your device
- You can clear chat history using the "Clear" button
- Uninstalling the extension removes all stored data

Contact: [your-email@example.com]
Last updated: February 2026
